  "title": "Marketing Executive #ESY",
  "description": "<p>•\tSupport marketing campaigns planning and execution</p><p>•\tResearch industry-related topics and prepare well-drafted drafts or copy for social media posts, promotional emails and other marketing collaterals</p><p>•\tDesign or assist in the creation of written, video, and image content for marketing channels to advertise our company and products</p><p>•\tManage social media channels including Instagram, Facebook, Xiao Hong Shu, WeChat, Tik Tok and assist in replying to any customer inquiries</p><p>•\tEnsure the collaterals created are consistent with the branding guidelines</p><p>•\tDesign customer success initiatives, or community events like fireside chats for customer engagement through Whatsapp channel</p><p>•\tPlan lead generation events with key partners</p><p>•\tMeasure and report the results of marketing campaigns, social media ads and initiatives</p><p>•\tAssists in any other ad-hoc data entry or administrative tasks as requested by the management</p><p>•\tDesign and lead team in offline marketing efforts (such as banners, pillar ads) and exhibitions</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates, please email your resume to annasee@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p><p>Anna See Sing Yee</p><p>CEI Reg R25157535</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 99C4599</p><p></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p></p>",
